cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.SE, cs.SY

The paper discusses the architecture and security issues of 5G networks, which are primarily related to networking and security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses potential security issues, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also mentions techniques such as network slicing, NFV, and SDN, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
